=head1 DESCRIPTION

Provides information about a WAF rule. This rule specifies the web
requests that you want to allow, block, or count.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 MetricName => Str

The name of the metrics for this rule.


=head2 Name => Str

A descriptive name for the rule.


=head2 PredicateList => ArrayRef[L<Paws::SecurityHub::AwsWafRulePredicateListDetails>]

Specifies the C<ByteMatchSet>, C<IPSet>, C<SqlInjectionMatchSet>,
C<XssMatchSet>, C<RegexMatchSet>, C<GeoMatchSet>, and
C<SizeConstraintSet> objects that you want to add to a rule and, for
each object, indicates whether you want to negate the settings.


